Package: inventoRy
Type: Package
Title: Performs a Variety of Inventory Calculations
Version: 0.1.0
Author: John Patrick Saldanha
Maintainer: John Patrick Saldanha <johnpsaldanha@gmail.com>
Description: The  inventoRy package offers the conventional textbook expressions
    and nonparametric bootstrap approaches for estimating inventory policy decisions 
    such as the reorder point and safety stocks for single item inevtories under the 
    continuous review inventory policy using either the cycle service level or fill 
    rate targets.
